final_desc: - Gading dikerjakan dan barang dari gading :Gading, tulang, tempurung kura-kura, tanduk, tanduk rusa, koral, kulit kerang dan bahan ukiran hewani lainnya dikerjakan, serta barang dari bahan tersebut (termasuk barang yang diperoleh melalui pencetakan).;- Worked ivory and articles of ivory :Worked ivory, bone, tortoise-shell, horn, antlers, coral, mother-of-pearl and other animal carving material, and articles of these materials (including articles obtained by moulding).

- Lain-lain :Gading, tulang, tempurung kura-kura, tanduk, tanduk rusa, koral, kulit kerang dan bahan ukiran hewani lainnya dikerjakan, serta barang dari bahan tersebut (termasuk barang yang diperoleh melalui pencetakan).;- Other :Worked ivory, bone, tortoise-shell, horn, antlers, coral, mother-of-pearl and other animal carving material, and articles of these materials (including articles obtained by moulding).
